#############################################################################
# Name: DarkDesktop
# Needed by:
#	Crystal:desktop/*
#	Crystal:panels/*
# Notes:
#	Orginal theme created by fRiQ
#############################################################################
# Description:
# This file is a collection of colorsets for FVWM. Because colorsets
# management is very simple and they use some space in memory (depending on
# desktop/wallpaper size), there is limited number of colorsets.
# Crystal uses colorsets from 0 to 9, however colorset 0 is reserved for
# QuakeConsole; it can be used elsewhere anyway (it's all black). If you want
# to create your own colorsets and use them, you can start at number 10; if
# you would like to make a colorset for Crystal, please use colorsets from
# numbers 1-9, so others can switch between colorsets without need to change
# other configuration options.
# If you want to know more about colorsets, please read FvwmTheme(1).
#
# Here is list of all colorsets and where they are used:
#
# Colorset 1
#	Foreground - text color in:
#		FvwmButtons
#		FvwmIdent
#		FvwmIconMan
#		FvwmForm
#	Background - border color in:
#		FvwmButtons
#		FvwmIdent
#		FvwmPager
#		FvwmIconMan
#	Tint - background color in:
#		FvwmButtons
#		FvwmIdent
#		FvwmForm
#		FvwmIconMan (normal and icon)
#
# Colorset 2
#	Foreground - color of page separators in FvwmPager
#	Tint - background color in FvwmPager
#
# Colorset 3
#	Tint - background color of selected page in FvwmPager
#
# Colorset 4
#	Foreground - text color in:
#		inactive window titlebars
#		inactive FvwmIconMan buttons
#	Background - border color of inactive windows
#	Highlight - color of 'sticky bars' on inactive windows
#	Shadow - color of 'sticky bard' on inactive windows
#	Tint - background color in:
#		inactive window titlebars
#		inactive FvwmIconMan buttons
#
# Colorset 5
#	Foreground - text color in:
#		active window titlebars
#		active FvwmIconMan buttons
#	Background - border color of active windows
#	Highlight - color of 'sticky bars' on active windows
#	Shadow - color of 'sticky bars' on active windows
#	Tint - background color in:
#		active window titlebars
#		active FvwmIconMan buttons
#
# Colorset 6
#	Foreground - text color of selected FvwmIconMan buttons
#	Tint - background color of selected FvwmIconMan buttons
#
# Colorset 7
#	Foreground - text color in menus
#	Background - border color in menus
#	Highlight - border color in menus
#	Shadow - border color in menus
#	Tint - background color in menus
#
# Colorset 8
#	Foreground - text color of selected menu position
#	Background - background color if selected menu position
#
# Colorset 9
#	Foreground - text color of FvwmForm items
#	Background - background color of FvwmForm items
#	Highlight - border color of FvwmForm items
#	Shadow - border color of FvwmForm items
#	Tint - background color of FvwmForm items
#############################################################################

### Colorsets ###############################################################
CleanupColorsets
Colorset 1 Fg "white", Bg "black", RootTransparent, Tint "black" 50
Colorset 2 Fg "black", RootTransparent, Tint "black" 50
Colorset 3 RootTransparent, Tint "#000066" 50
Colorset 4 Fg "gray", Bg "black", Hi "gray", Sh "gray", \
	RootTransparent, Tint "black" 50
Colorset 5 Fg "white", Bg "black", Hi "gray", Sh "gray", \
	RootTransparent, Tint "blue" 50
Colorset 6 Fg "white", RootTransparent, Tint "#000066" 50
Colorset 7 Fg "white", Bg "black", Hi "black", Sh "black", \
	   RootTransparent, Tint "black" 50
Colorset 8 Fg "black", Bg "gray"
Colorset 9 Fg "white", Bg "black", Hi "gray", Sh "gray", \
	   RootTransparent, Tint "#222222" 50
#############################################################################

